* {{ill|Tenpaku Ward|ja|天白区|12=draft|12=draft}} - A ward of Nagoya named after the river.
* {{ill|Tenpaku Village (Aichi)|ja|天白村 (愛知県)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Formerly in Nagoya, named after the river.
* Tenpaku River - A small river in {{ill|Higashiura Town|ja|東浦町|12=draft|12=draft}}, also associated with the Tenpaku deity.<ref>{{Cite book|和書|title=張州府志 第6|year=1916|publisher=名古屋史談会}}</ref>
* {{ill|Tenpaku Town (Okazaki)|ja|天白町 (岡崎市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A town in {{ill|Okazaki|ja|岡崎市|12=draft|12=draft}}, named after the Tenpaku deity.
* {{ill|Tenpaku River (Tahara)|ja|天白川 (田原市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - A river flowing through {{ill|Tahara City|ja|田原市|12=draft|12=draft}}.

